{
  "stem": "18102.6",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I think that's the only message you can give, and you have to educate the young people, I think, is where this begins.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It doesn't begin with adults.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It begins at a much younger age.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Kids in their teens should know the difference and be told the difference.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I guess risk has a counterpart.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It's called reward.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "One doesn't take risks unless there is a reward.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Sugihara's reward was his self-esteem, his conscience, his, his religion, his belief in right from wrong.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Those are big rewards for a human being, because they serve a need-- an internal need, that give you great strength, without which I think you can't get anywhere.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And so I think that there is a definite risk-reward of that kind for every individual that understands the difference between hatred and a savior or saving lives.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I don't think it's so difficult a message.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I don't think that it's so difficult to understand that the reward is much greater than the risks involved and well-worth the risk involved.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Sugihara is not alone, as I say.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "There are others, and there's probably countless of different kinds of others that helped save lives during the Holocaust, whose names we'll never know, whether they saved one, or two, or a handful.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We just know the standouts.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We know the, the people who saved in the thousands of people.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But there were others, and I think we have to show those stories as well, to show that the risks that they took were rewarded in their lives, and I think it were-- yeah, I think it was.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I can only contemplate and hope that the answer is yes.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "One doesn't know what one's moral strengths are in, in a moment of difficulty until you're there.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
